data.description: Welcome home! Beautifully updated home with over 4200+ square feet perfect for elegant living and entertaining in the coveted Bardmoor North subdivision near the golf course.  This stunning home is set on a cul-de-sac with a tranquil pond in the backyard.  It features updated roof,  3 A/Cs, electrical panel and Smart Home connections, along with beautiful tile and molding details throughout the home.  French door entry leads to an exquisite foyer and living room with separate formal dining room, and sunken fireplace seating area, with high ceilings and recessed lighting throughout.  Beautiful white cabinetry, stainless steel appliances, natural stone-quatzite countertops and double wall oven offer a superb kitchen space.  The roomy cooking island and large walk-in pantry will elevate your food prep experience.  The in-kitchen dining space and stained glass windows create a wonderful space for cooking and eating.  The elegant hallway leads to the  4 Bedrooms including a spacious master bedroom with view of the pond and completely remodeled ensuite bathroom.   The white marble tile and chandeliers add sophistication to the airy bathroom with separate oversized glass shower and double sinks.  It is a perfect space for relaxing in the modern freestanding tub.    Spacious bedrooms each have great features to meet your needs for family, guests and office space.  The family room features walls of windows and overlooks spacious screened in pool area by the water.  It features ceiling fans and generous space for relaxing and entertaining.  The backyard is beautifully landscaped with sprinkler system on well water and fully fenced.  The property is oversized and includes part of the pond.  Circular driveway  and oversized two car garage offers a separate space for golf cart parking, which has been converted into a workshop area.  Expansive closet space throughout the home, oversized pantry, laundry room and walk-up attic means you will never want for storage space.   This house has been updated with style and care and has it all!  With NO FLOOD insurance required -X zone designation.
